ACADEMIC PROJECT NOTICE

This repository contains an academic project completed as part of graduate 
coursework at Illinois Institute of Technology (ITMM 586 - Information 
Technology Auditing, Fall 2025).

While based on publicly available information, the specific audit findings, 
test results, and recommendations are hypothetical and created for educational 
purposes. This does not represent an actual audit engagement with Collins 
Aerospace or RTX Corporation.

All analysis is based on:
- Publicly available SEC filings and news reports
- Industry standard security frameworks (COBIT, NIST, CMMC)
- Academic research and case study methodology
- No confidential or proprietary information was accessed

The findings and recommendations should not be construed as actual security 
assessments for Collins Aerospace.
